message.text:
IABF Tamaraws, MarkProf Batch 22 Awaits You! ✨

The FEU IABF Student Council, through the STRAW External Affairs, in partnership with MarkProf Foundation, Inc., proudly invites you to the MarkProf Bootcamp Roadshow on September 21, 2025 (7:00 PM – 8:30 PM).

For two decades, MarkProf has been shaping future leaders—training over 500 top students who now lead in market innovation and nation-building across major organizations. Each year, hundreds of applicants nationwide aspire to join the prestigious free 8-weekend Marketing and Sales Bootcamp—but only 25 young marketing leaders make it through the rigorous selection process.

Don’t miss this chance to learn more about the MarkProf journey and get tips on how to ace the application process from MarkProf alumni themselves.

Join the event here: https://bit.ly/MP22Online

#SoaringGreaterHeights

message.text:
IABF Tamaraws, MarkProf Batch 22 Awaits You! ✨

The FEU IABF Student Council, through the STRAW External Affairs, in partnership with MarkProf Foundation, Inc., proudly invites you to the MarkProf Bootcamp Roadshow on September 21, 2025 (7:00 PM – 8:30 PM).

For two decades, MarkProf has been shaping future leaders—training over 500 top students who now lead in market innovation and nation-building across major organizations. Each year, hundreds of applicants nationwide aspire to join the prestigious free 8-weekend Marketing and Sales Bootcamp—but only 25 young marketing leaders make it through the rigorous selection process.

Don’t miss this chance to learn more about the MarkProf journey and get tips on how to ace the application process from MarkProf alumni themselves.

Join the event here: https://bit.ly/MP22Online

#SoaringGreaterHeights

message.text:
This day is for our DAY’3rs! 

As we wrap up the last day of our event, we want to make sure it’s not just the students who are celebrated, but also our beloved DIAR’s. This is a moment to give back and bring them a joy, spark hope, and let them feel that today, it’s their time to shine. 

Seeing their smiles is a beautiful reminder to the Campus Ministry of why we do what we do. It’s our simple way of showing how much they matter.

Maraming salamat po sa tuwa at sayang hatid ninyo sa FEU Campus Ministry mga Ates and kuyas!

RCAM Ministry on Campus
ACY - Manila

#rcamcampusministryawarenessweek2025
#feu_campus_ministry
#sa_feucm_ako

message.text:
This day is for our DAY’3rs! 

As we wrap up the last day of our event, we want to make sure it’s not just the students who are celebrated, but also our beloved DIAR’s. This is a moment to give back and bring them a joy, spark hope, and let them feel that today, it’s their time to shine. 

Seeing their smiles is a beautiful reminder to the Campus Ministry of why we do what we do. It’s our simple way of showing how much they matter.

Maraming salamat po sa tuwa at sayang hatid ninyo sa FEU Campus Ministry mga Ates and kuyas!

RCAM Ministry on Campus
ACY - Manila

message.text:
This day is for our DAY’3rs! 

As we wrap up the last day of our event, we want to make sure it’s not just the students who are celebrated, but also our beloved DIAR’s. This is a moment to give back and bring them a joy, spark hope, and let them feel that today, it’s their time to shine. 

Seeing their smiles is a beautiful reminder to the Campus Ministry of why we do what we do. It’s our simple way of showing how much they matter.

Maraming salamat po sa tuwa at sayang hatid ninyo sa FEU Campus Ministry mga Ates and kuyas!

RCAM Ministry on Campus
ACY - Manila

#rcamcampusministryawarenessweek2025
#feu_campus_ministry
#sa_feucm_ako

message.text:
This day is for our DAY’3rs! 

As we wrap up the last day of our event, we want to make sure it’s not just the students who are celebrated, but also our beloved DIAR’s. This is a moment to give back and bring them a joy, spark hope, and let them feel that today, it’s their time to shine. 

Seeing their smiles is a beautiful reminder to the Campus Ministry of why we do what we do. It’s our simple way of showing how much they matter.

Maraming salamat po sa tuwa at sayang hatid ninyo sa FEU Campus Ministry mga Ates and kuyas!

RCAM Ministry on Campus
ACY - Manila

#rcamcampusministryawarenessweek2025
#feu_campus_ministry
#sa_feucm_ako

message.text:
This day is for our DAY’3rs! 

As we wrap up the last day of our event, we want to make sure it’s not just the students who are celebrated, but also our beloved DIAR’s. This is a moment to give back and bring them a joy, spark hope, and let them feel that today, it’s their time to shine. 

Seeing their smiles is a beautiful reminder to the Campus Ministry of why we do what we do. It’s our simple way of showing how much they matter.

Maraming salamat po sa tuwa at sayang hatid ninyo sa FEU Campus Ministry mga Ates and kuyas!

RCAM Ministry on Campus
ACY - Manila

#rcamcampusministryawarenessweek2025
#feu_campus_ministry
#sa_feucm_ako

message.text:
This day is for our DAY’3rs! 

As we wrap up the last day of our event, we want to make sure it’s not just the students who are celebrated, but also our beloved DIAR’s. This is a moment to give back and bring them a joy, spark hope, and let them feel that today, it’s their time to shine. 

Seeing their smiles is a beautiful reminder to the Campus Ministry of why we do what we do. It’s our simple way of showing how much they matter.

Maraming salamat po sa tuwa at sayang hatid ninyo sa FEU Campus Ministry mga Ates and kuyas!

RCAM Ministry on Campus
ACY - Manila

#rcamcampusministryawarenessweek2025
#feu_campus_ministry
#sa_feucm_ako
